Bomber- (5)
- The bomber can place a total of 3 bombs at people's houses to kill them. They can place a bomb every night and once placed, the locations cannot be changed.
- If the Bomber is ever killed by a member of another faction, all the other people they have chosen will be weak attacked. These attacks are not counted as visits.
- The bomber can place new bombs once they have died and respawned. The bomber dying because of tribute will not trigger their ability.
- Placing a bomb is night end and is counted as a visit, and the targets are killed at the same time as when the bomber is killed.
- Respawns in 6 phases.
